CardanoBudzMay4th.name: Cardano Budz Skywalker OG
description: Happy May the 4th!  You have received a rare token
to commemorate the first May the 4th on Cardano in
the Mary Era.  This token is the first draft of our
Cardano Budz avatar.  Launching later this year will
be the first drop, where we will create unique tokens
with randomized artifacts.  The Cardano Budz mascot
should bring awareness to Marijuana Law reform, and
safe access for medical and recreational use.  Keep
up to date on our roadmap at https://CardanoBudz.io.
